metadata.name: Original 1/1 PantherFlies
metadata.description:
Original 1/1 NFT 2160 x 1620px 300dpi  
ERC721 Contract

This is a 100% digital art piece created by Kailene Piazza using procreate.

A person's words do not define them, their actions do. A name is just a name; a breath of air you speak in their presence. Who they are and what they do is entirely a different matter. When someone offers a hand to help and expects something in return does not mean every person you meet will expect something of you.

When someone offers you a hand to help, and then expects something in return, that does not mean every person you meet will expect something of you.

Just because someone looks intimidating, that doesn’t mean they are, and just because someone appears innocent, that doesn’t mean that they aren’t a monster. Again, only their actions define them. All of these things are what PantherFlies are based. We are a society of judging first and understanding later. Do not judge a book by its cover. What lies within may certainly surprise you.

Utility
